@startuml 05-create-contact
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Create Contact

actor User
participant "AddContactPage" as UI
participant "ContactsApi" as SVC
participant "POST /api/contacts" as API
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
queue "Channel<EmbeddingJob>" as Q
database "contacts" as DB

User -> UI: fill form, tap Save
UI -> SVC: create(payload)
SVC -> API: POST CreateContactRequest
API -> API: validate (lengths, caps)
API -> API: OwnerUserId = currentUser.Id
API -> CTX: Contacts.Add(contact)
API -> CTX: SaveChangesAsync
CTX -> DB: INSERT contact
DB --> CTX: id
API -> Q: Write(EmbeddingJob{contactId})
API --> SVC: 201 ContactDto\nLocation: /api/contacts/{id}
SVC --> UI: dto
UI -> UI: router.navigate(/contacts/:id)
UI --> User: toast "Contact added"\ndetail screen renders

@enduml
